Config keyboard
-----------------

    localectl set-keymap us-intl
    localectl set-x11-keymap us intl
    setxkbmap -layout us -variant intl

2) Config /etc/X11/xorg.conf

Section "Device"
	Identifier "Intel Graphics"
	Driver	   "Intel"
	Option     "Backlight"  "intel_backlight"
EndSection


